   167→### Un / Escape
   168→
   169→Turn the given string into a safe to  
   170→use key or value in your INI file.
   171→
   172→```js
   173→safe(`"unsafe string"`) // -> \"unsafe string\"
   174→```
   175→
   176→Or reverse the process with:
   177→
   178→```js
   179→unsafe(`\\"safe string\\"`) // -> "safe string"
   180→```
